<h2>Confirm your kit claim</h2>


Your kit has been located in our records. Please double check that the following information is correct:


<p>
<strong>Kit name</strong><br/>
<%= @kit.name %>
</p>
<p>
<strong>Study name</strong><br/>
<%= @kit.study.name %>
</p>
<p>
<strong>Kit contents:</strong><br/>
<table class="admin_table">
  <tr>
    <th>Sample ID</th>
    <th>Kit name</th>
    <th>Sample name</th>
  </tr>
  <% @kit.samples.sort { |a,b| a.original_kit_design_sample.sort_order <=> b.original_kit_design_sample.sort_order }.each do |s| %>
    <tr class="<%= cycle 'even', 'odd' %>">
      <td><%= s.crc_id %></td>
      <td><%= @kit.name %></td>
      <td><%= s.name %></td>
    </tr>
  <% end %>
</table>
</p>

<p><strong>Legal</strong><br/>

You acknowledge and agree that you will use this kit to collect and submit only
your saliva to the Personal Genome Project, and that you will neither collect
nor submit the saliva of any other person, whether in your own name or on
behalf of any other person. Your participation in the Personal Genome Project,
including this saliva collection opportunity, is governed by the PGP's <a
href="http://www.personalgenomes.org/tos.html">Terms of Service</a> and
<a href="http://www.personalgenomes.org/consent/">informed consent agreement</a>. 
Failure to be abide by these terms may result in your removal from the project.
</p>

<%= form_tag kit_confirm_claim_path(@kit), :method => 'post' do %>
  <div class="field">
    <%= check_box_tag :agreed, nil, params[:agreed] -%> I agree<p/>
    <%= submit_tag("Confirm", :name => nil) %>
  </div>
  </p>
<% end %>


